Q) WHAT IS INCIDENT?

ANSWER:

When a user creates new incident, it appears in the incident list with the state set to new.

When the incident is assigned to the support group or an individual it updated statues with assigned.

When the assigned user start working on the incident. The state is updated to “In Progress”.

If assigned user need additional information, change state to awaited and request additional information from user.

If assigned user don;t know how to resolve incident, assign to L3 team(dev team).

if assigned user know how to resolve incident, provide solution and update state to resolved.

After confirmation from the user, the incident state is updated to closed state.

